{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01WekmSXGn4JNbzkgRELFy3p","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now let me compile the complete inventory for you:\n\n## Complete Wallet Package Inventory\n\n**Location:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/wallet/src/`\n\n---\n\n### **1. Main Entry Point**\n\n#### **`index.ts`** (1-57)\n**Exports:**\n- Context: `WalletContext` (line 2)\n- Core hooks: `useWallet`, `useBalance` (lines 5-6)\n- Types: `WalletState`, `WalletContextValue` (line 7)\n- Mock wallet: `MockWalletProvider`, `DEFAULT_MOCK_CONFIG`, `MockConfig` (lines 10-11)\n- Real wallet: `RealWalletProvider` (line 14)\n- Test wallet: `TestWalletProvider` (line 17)\n- Main provider: `WalletProvider` (line 20)\n- Balance utils: `solToLamports`, `lamportsToSol`, `formatAmount`, `formatAmountCompact`, etc. (lines 23-32)\n- Transaction management: `TransactionProvider`, `useTransaction`, types (lines 36-44)\n- Treasury utilities: `FEE_CONSTANTS`, `calculateFee`, etc. (lines 47-56)\n\n**Key Imports:** None (pure re-export file)\n\n---\n\n### **2. Core Provider & Mode Switching**\n\n#### **`WalletProvider.tsx`** (1-54)\n**Key Component:** `WalletProvider` (lines 42-54)\n**Key Functions:**\n- `getRpcUrl()` (lines 17-23) - reads `VITE_RPC_URL` env var\n- `isMockMode()` (lines 29-36) - reads `VITE_MOCK_MODE` env var (default: true)\n\n**Delegation Logic (lines 45-51):**\n- If `isMockMode()` → renders `<MockWalletProvider>` \n- Otherwise → lazy-loads `<RealWalletProvider>` in `<Suspense>`\n- Both wrapped in `<ConnectionProvider endpoint={endpoint}>` (line 53)\n\n**Important Imports:**\n- `ConnectionProvider` from `@solana/wallet-adapter-react` (line 2)\n- `MockWalletProvider` from `./mock` (line 3)\n- Lazy-loads `RealWalletProvider` from `./real/RealWalletProvider` (lines 6-10)\n\n**Environment Variables:**\n- `VITE_RPC_URL` (line 20) - defaults to `\"https://api.devnet.solana.com\"` (line 15)\n- `VITE_MOCK_MODE` (line 32) - defaults to `true` when unset/empty/`\"true\"` (line 35)\n\n---\n\n### **3. Real Wallet Implementation**\n\n#### **`real/RealWalletProvider.tsx`** (1-121)\n**Key Component:** `RealWalletProvider` (lines 99-120)\n**Internal Bridge:** `WalletBridge` (lines 27-93)\n\n**Key Functions:**\n- `getCluster()` (lines 14-21) - reads `VITE_SOLANA_NETWORK` (defaults to `\"devnet\"`)\n- `connect()` (lines 32-40) - opens Unified Wallet modal if no wallet selected\n- `disconnect()` (lines 42-44)\n- `sendTransaction()` (lines 46-55)\n- `signMessage()` (lines 57-65)\n\n**Architecture:**\n- Uses `UnifiedWalletProvider` from `@jup-ag/wallet-adapter` (lines 103-116)\n- `WalletBridge` reads from `useAdapterWallet()` and `useUnifiedWalletContext()` (lines 28, 30)\n- Maps adapter state to `WalletContextValue` (lines 67-88)\n- Provides via `WalletContext.Provider` (line 91)\n\n**Important Imports:**\n- `useConnection`, `useWallet as useAdapterWallet` from `@solana/wallet-adapter-react` (lines 4-6)\n- `UnifiedWalletProvider`, `useUnifiedWalletContext` from `@jup-ag/wallet-adapter` (lines 8-10)\n- `WalletContext` from `../context` (line 11)\n\n**ConnectionProvider:** Assumed to be in parent (from `WalletProvider.tsx`)\n\n---\n\n#### **`real/index.ts`** (1-1)\n**Exports:** `RealWalletProvider` (line 1)\n\n---\n\n### **4. Mock Wallet Implementation**\n\n#### **`mock/MockWalletProvider.tsx`** (1-187)\n**Key Component:** `MockWalletProvider` (lines 31-186)\n\n**Key Functions:**\n- `connect()` (lines 71-105) - simulated latency, generates/loads keypair, sets balance\n- `disconnect()` (lines 107-115) - clears state (optionally preserves localStorage)\n- `sendTransaction()` (lines 117-134) - 500ms delay, 5% random failure, returns mock signature\n- `signMessage()` (lines 136-150) - returns random 64-byte signature\n- `updateBalance()` (lines 153-155) - mock-only, modifies balance\n- `getBalance()` (lines 157-159) - mock-only, returns SOL\n- `getBalanceLamports()` (lines 161-163) - mock-only, returns lamports\n\n**State Management:**\n- Loads persisted state on mount (lines 43-59)\n- Persists state changes to localStorage (lines 62-69)\n- Local state: `state: WalletState`, `balanceLamports: number` (lines 37-40)\n\n**Config Options (MockConfig):**\n- `initialBalance` (SOL)\n- `autoConnect` (boolean)\n- `simulatedLatency` (ms)\n- `persistState` (boolean)\n\n**Important Imports:**\n- `PublicKey`, `Transaction` from `@solana/web3.js` (line 2)\n- `WalletContext` from `../context` (line 3)\n- Mock utilities from `./MockWalletState` (lines 6-17)\n\n**Context Value:** Extended `WalletContextValue` with `updateBalance`, `getBalance`, `getBalanceLamports`, `isMock: true` (lines 166-181)\n\n---\n\n#### **`mock/MockWalletState.ts`** (1-82)\n**Key Exports:**\n- `MockConfig` interface (lines 3-8)\n- `DEFAULT_MOCK_CONFIG` (lines 10-15) - 1000 SOL, no autoConnect, 500ms latency, persist enabled\n- `createMockKeypair()` (lines 24-26)\n- `loadPersistedState()` (lines 28-39) - from localStorage key `\"rng-utopia-mock-wallet\"`\n- `persistState()` (lines 41-48)\n- `clearPersistedState()` (lines 50-57)\n- `generateMockSignature()` (lines 59-65) - returns 64-byte hex string\n- `delay()` (lines 67-69)\n- `solToLamports()` (lines 71-73)\n- `lamportsToSol()` (lines 75-77)\n- `getPublicKeyFromAddress()` (lines 79-81)\n\n**Storage Key:** `\"rng-utopia-mock-wallet\"` (line 17)\n\n**Important Imports:**\n- `Keypair`, `PublicKey` from `@solana/web3.js` (line 1)\n\n---\n\n#### **`mock/index.ts`** (1-8)\n**Exports:**\n- `MockWalletProvider` (line 1)\n- `MockConfig`, `DEFAULT_MOCK_CONFIG`, `solToLamports`, `lamportsToSol`, `generateMockSignature` (lines 2-8)\n\n---\n\n### **5. Test Wallet Implementation**\n\n#### **`test/TestWalletProvider.tsx`** (1-119)\n**Key Component:** `TestWalletProvider` (lines 27-118)\n\n**Purpose:** E2E testing against local test-validator with real Keypair (no browser extension)\n\n**Props:**\n- `keypair: Keypair` (required) (line 16)\n- `rpcUrl?: string` (defaults to `\"http://127.0.0.1:8899\"`) (lines 17-18, 11)\n- `autoConnect?: boolean` (defaults to `true`) (line 20)\n\n**Key Functions:**\n- `connect()` (lines 41-50) - verifies keypair by checking balance\n- `disconnect()` (lines 52-54)\n- `sendTransaction()` (lines 56-70) - uses `sendAndConfirmTransaction` with injected keypair\n- `signMessage()` (lines 72-83) - returns deterministic signature from keypair's secret key\n\n**Auto-connect:** Effect on lines 86-90 connects on mount if `autoConnect=true`\n\n**Important Imports:**\n- `Connection`, `Keypair`, `Transaction`, `sendAndConfirmTransaction` from `@solana/web3.js` (lines 2-7)\n- `WalletContext` from `../context` (line 8)\n\n**Context Value:** `WalletContextValue` with `isMock: false` (lines 92-113)\n\n**Note:** Does NOT wrap children in `ConnectionProvider` (creates own `Connection` instance on line 36-39)\n\n---\n\n#### **`test/index.ts`** (1-2)\n**Exports:** `TestWalletProvider` (line 1)\n\n---\n\n#### **`test/TestWalletProvider.test.tsx`** (1-69)\n**Test File:** Unit tests for TestWalletProvider and MockWalletProvider\n\n**Tests:**\n1. **TestWalletProvider** (lines 27-51):\n   - Auto-connects and exposes publicKey matching the keypair\n   - Verifies `connected`, `publicKey`, `address`, `isMock: false`\n\n2. **MockWalletProvider** (lines 53-68):\n   - Starts disconnected by default\n   - Verifies initial state, `isMock: true`\n\n**Mocking:**\n- Mocks `@solana/web3.js` Connection.getBalance (lines 10-24) to return 1 SOL\n\n**Important Imports:**\n- Vitest testing utils (line 1)\n- `@testing-library/react` (line 2)\n- `Keypair` from `@solana/web3.js` (line 3)\n- Test and Mock providers (lines 4-5)\n- `useWallet` hook (line 6)\n\n---\n\n### **6. Core Context & Hooks**\n\n#### **`context.ts`** (1-4)\n**Exports:** `WalletContext` (created via `createContext<WalletContextValue | null>(null)`)\n\n---\n\n#### **`types.ts`** (1-24)\n**Key Types:**\n\n**`WalletState`** (lines 3-8):\n- `connected: boolean`\n- `connecting: boolean`\n- `address: string | null`\n- `publicKey: PublicKey | null`\n\n**`WalletContextValue`** (lines 10-23) extends `WalletState`:\n- `connect: () => Promise<void>`\n- `disconnect: () => Promise<void>`\n- `sendTransaction: (transaction: Transaction) => Promise<string>`\n- `signMessage: (message: Uint8Array) => Promise<Uint8Array>`\n- `isMock?: boolean` (line 16) - mock/test indicator\n- `getBalance?: () => number` (line 18) - mock-only, returns SOL\n- `getBalanceLamports?: () => number` (line 20) - mock-only, returns lamports\n- `updateBalance?: (deltaLamports: number) => void` (line 22) - mock-only\n\n**Important Imports:**\n- `PublicKey`, `Transaction` from `@solana/web3.js` (line 1)\n\n---\n\n#### **`useWallet.ts`** (1-11)\n**Key Hook:** `useWallet()` (lines 5-11)\n\n**Behavior:**\n- Returns `useContext(WalletContext)`\n- Throws error if used outside `WalletProvider` (line 8)\n\n**Important Imports:**\n- `useContext` from `react` (line 1)\n- `WalletContext` from `./context` (line 2)\n\n---\n\n#### **`useBalance.ts`** (1-135)\n**Key Hook:** `useBalance(options?: UseBalanceOptions)` (lines 33-134)\n\n**Options:**\n- `pollInterval?: number` (default: 10000ms) (lines 27-29)\n\n**Returns (`BalanceResult`):**\n- `balance: number | null` (SOL) (line 9)\n- `balanceLamports: number | null` (line 11)\n- `loading: boolean` (line 13)\n- `error: Error | null` (line 15)\n- `refresh: () => Promise<void>` (line 17)\n- `formatted: string | null` (line 19) - e.g., \"1.2345\"\n- `formattedCompact: string | null` (line 21) - e.g., \"1.2k\"\n- `lastUpdated: Date | null` (line 23)\n\n**Behavior:**\n- Fetches mock balance via `getMockBalance()` if `isMock=true` (lines 59-62)\n- Otherwise fetches from RPC via `connection.getBalance()` (lines 64-67)\n- Polls at `pollInterval` (lines 99-100)\n- Resets on disconnect (lines 88-92)\n\n**Important Imports:**\n- `useState`, `useEffect`, `useCallback`, `useRef` from `react` (line 1)\n- `LAMPORTS_PER_SOL` from `@solana/web3.js` (line 2)\n- `useConnection` from `@solana/wallet-adapter-react` (line 3)\n- `useWallet` from `./useWallet` (line 4)\n- `formatAmount`, `formatAmountCompact` from `./balance` (line 5)\n\n**ConnectionProvider usage:** Calls `useConnection()` from `@solana/wallet-adapter-react` (line 38)\n\n---\n\n#### **`hooks.ts`** (1-6)\n**Exports:**\n- `useWallet` (line 2)\n- `useBalance` (line 3)\n- `useConnection` from `@solana/wallet-adapter-react` (line 4)\n- Types: `BalanceResult`, `WalletState`, `WalletContextValue` (lines 5-6)\n\n**Note:** Lightweight hooks entry point with no provider dependencies\n\n---\n\n### **7. Balance Utilities**\n\n#### **`balance/formatBalance.ts`** (1-83)\n**Key Functions:**\n- `formatAmount(lamports, precision=2)` (lines 6-9) - e.g., \"1.23\"\n- `formatAmountCompact(lamports)` (lines 14-21) - e.g., \"1.2k\", \"1.5M\"\n- `lamportsToSOL(lamports)` (lines 27-29) - legacy conversion\n- `SOLToLamports(sol)` (lines 34-36) - returns `bigint`\n- `formatBalanceDisplay(lamports, options)` (lines 41-60) - with $ prefix, compact/precision options\n- `parseSOLInput(input)` (lines 66-75) - parses string to lamports, returns `bigint | null`\n- `isValidSOLAmount(input)` (lines 80-82) - validates SOL input string\n\n**Important Imports:**\n- `LAMPORTS_PER_SOL` from `@solana/web3.js` (line 1)\n\n---\n\n#### **`balance/index.ts`** (1-9)\n**Exports:** All functions from `formatBalance.ts`\n\n---\n\n### **8. Transaction Management**\n\n#### **`transactions/TransactionProvider.tsx`** (1-101)\n**Key Component:** `TransactionProvider` (lines 45-92)\n**Key Hook:** `useTransaction()` (lines 94-100)\n\n**Context Value (`TransactionContextValue`):**\n- `state: TransactionState` (line 27)\n- `submit: (transaction) => Promise<string>` (line 28)\n- `reset: () => void` (line 29)\n- `isProcessing: boolean` (line 30)\n\n**Transaction Status:** `\"idle\" | \"building\" | \"signing\" | \"submitting\" | \"confirming\" | \"confirmed\" | \"failed\"` (lines 11-18)\n\n**TransactionState:**\n- `status: TransactionStatus`\n- `signature: string | null`\n- `error: Error | null`\n\n**Behavior:**\n- `submit()` (lines 49-69) - delegates to `wallet.sendTransaction()`, transitions through statuses\n- Note: Confirmation waiting not yet implemented (line 58 comment)\n\n**Important Imports:**\n- `createContext`, `useContext`, `useState`, `useCallback` from `react` (lines 1-7)\n- `Transaction` from `@solana/web3.js` (line 8)\n- `useWallet` from `../useWallet` (line 9)\n\n---\n\n#### **`transactions/index.ts`** (1-9)\n**Exports:** `TransactionProvider`, `useTransaction`, types\n\n---\n\n### **9. Treasury Constants**\n\n#### **`treasury/constants.ts`** (1-96)\n**Key Exports:**\n\n**`FEE_CONSTANTS`** (lines 4-13):\n- `TOTAL_BPS: 300` (3%)\n- `PLATFORM_REVENUE_BPS: 200` (2%)\n- `CASHBACK_POOL_BPS: 50` (0.5%)\n- `REWARDS_BUDGET_BPS: 50` (0.5%)\n\n**`FEE_BREAKDOWN`** (lines 16-21): Display-friendly version\n\n**`LIMITS`** (lines 24-31):\n- `MAX_FEE_BPS: 1000` (10%)\n- `MAX_BET_LAMPORTS: 1_000_000_000_000n` (1000 SOL)\n- `MAX_PLAYERS_PER_ROUND: 10_000`\n\n**`PROGRAM_IDS`** (lines 34-41): Placeholder PublicKeys (all `11111...`)\n\n**`TREASURY_ADDRESSES`** (lines 44-55): Placeholder addresses for mainnet/devnet\n\n**Functions:**\n- `calculateFee(poolTotalLamports)` (lines 60-62) - returns fee amount\n- `calculatePayout(poolTotalLamports)` (lines 67-70) - returns pool minus fee\n- `calculateFeeBreakdown(poolTotalLamports)` (lines 75-95) - returns breakdown object\n\n**Important Imports:**\n- `PublicKey` from `@solana/web3.js` (line 1)\n\n---\n\n#### **`treasury/index.ts`** (1-10)\n**Exports:** All constants and functions from `constants.ts`\n\n---\n\n### **10. Package Configuration**\n\n#### **`package.json`** (1-47)\n**Package:** `@rng-utopia/wallet` v0.1.0\n\n**Exports Map:**\n- `.` → `./src/index.ts`\n- `./mock` → `./src/mock/index.ts`\n- `./real` → `./src/real/index.ts`\n- `./test` → `./src/test/index.ts`\n- `./context` → `./src/context.ts`\n- `./hooks` → `./src/hooks.ts`\n\n**Scripts:**\n- `lint`, `lint:fix`, `typecheck`, `test` (vitest)\n\n**Key Dependencies:**\n- `@jup-ag/wallet-adapter: ^0.2.6` (line 26)\n- `@solana/wallet-adapter-base: ^0.9.23` (line 27)\n- `@solana/wallet-adapter-react: ^0.15.35` (line 28)\n- `@solana/web3.js: ^1.98.0` (line 29)\n- `react: ^18.3.1` (line 30)\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n### **Architecture Flow:**\n\n1. **Mode Detection:** `WalletProvider.tsx` checks `VITE_MOCK_MODE` (default: true)\n2. **Mock Mode:** Uses `MockWalletProvider` (localStorage persistence, simulated latency)\n3. **Real Mode:** Lazy-loads `RealWalletProvider` → wraps `UnifiedWalletProvider` (@jup-ag) → bridges to `WalletContext`\n4. **Test Mode:** `TestWalletProvider` for E2E with injected Keypair (no extension)\n\n### **Key Environment Variables:**\n- `VITE_MOCK_MODE` (default: `true`) - toggles mock vs real\n- `VITE_RPC_URL` (default: `\"https://api.devnet.solana.com\"`)\n- `VITE_SOLANA_NETWORK` (default: `\"devnet\"`) - used by RealWalletProvider\n\n### **ConnectionProvider Usage:**\n- `WalletProvider.tsx` wraps both mock and real with `<ConnectionProvider endpoint={rpcUrl}>`\n- `useBalance.ts` calls `useConnection()` from `@solana/wallet-adapter-react`\n- `TestWalletProvider` creates its own `Connection` instance (no wrapper)\n\n### **Test Coverage:**\n- 1 test file: `src/test/TestWalletProvider.test.tsx`\n- Tests both TestWalletProvider and MockWalletProvider basics\n- Uses vitest + @testing-library/react"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: adfd387 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 47645\ntool_uses: 25\nduration_ms: 119955</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0f6af63c-d689-426d-9dd8-218925b8488a","uuid":"d3d7eaf4-da79-48ea-bbf0-cf92044bd5c1","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Thoroughly inventory the wallet package at `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/wallet/src/`. I need:\n\n1. All source files and their key exports/functions (with l