latform/e2e/visual/routes.spec.ts`\n\n**Test Suite: Route baselines (lines 3-63)**\n- Contains 11 route baseline tests (home, coinflip, lord-of-rngs, close-call, crash, game-of-trades, profile, quests, loot, fairness, leaderboard, 404)\n- Takes full-page screenshots of each route\n- Uses `stablePage` fixture for determinism\n- **Does not explicitly test wallet functionality but wallet icon is visible in all routes**\n\n#### 2.2 Real Mode Tests\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/real/startup.spec.ts`\n\n**Test Suite: Real mode startup (lines 27-72)**\n\n**Test 1: app loads without console errors and wallet icon renders disconnected (lines 28-44)**\n- **What It Verifies:**\n  - App loads without console errors\n  - Wallet icon is visible\n  - Wallet icon does NOT have connected class\n  - Balance displays \"—\" (em dash) for disconnected state\n- **Key Assertions:**\n  - `await expect(walletIcon).toBeVisible({ timeout: 10_000 })`\n  - `await expect(walletIcon).not.toHaveClass(/rpg-wallet-icon--connected/)`\n  - `await expect(amount).toHaveText(\"—\")`\n- **Selectors:**\n  - `.rpg-wallet-icon` (wallet icon)\n  - `.rpg-wallet-icon__amount` (balance display)\n\n**Test 2: clicking wallet icon calls connect without crashing (lines 46-71)**\n- **What It Verifies:**\n  - Clicking wallet icon triggers connect() without errors\n  - App remains functional after click\n  - Wallet icon and main app structure still visible\n- **Key Actions:**\n  - Clicks wallet icon\n  - Waits 1 second for processing\n  - Verifies wallet icon still visible\n  - Verifies main title still visible\n- **Key Assertions:**\n  - `await expect(walletIcon).toBeVisible()`\n  - `await expect(title).toBeVisible()`\n- **Selectors:**\n  - `.rpg-wallet-icon` (wallet icon)\n  - `.rpg-title` (main app title)\n\n**Test Fixture:** Uses custom `realPage` fixture (lines 8-25)\n- Collects console errors throughout test\n- Fails test if any console errors detected\n- Does NOT freez