e numbers for all findings.","agentId":"ace59ee","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now let me compile all the findings into a comprehensive report.\n\n## Completion Report\n\nI found all test files relevant to the 205-real-wallet spec. Here's the complete inventory:\n\n### 1. Vitest Unit Tests (Wallet Package)\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/wallet/src/test/TestWalletProvider.test.tsx`\n\n**Test Suite 1: TestWalletProvider (lines 26-51)**\n- **Test Name:** \"auto-connects and exposes publicKey matching the keypair\"\n- **What It Verifies:**\n  - TestWalletProvider auto-connects on mount\n  - Connected state becomes true\n  - publicKey matches the injected keypair\n  - address matches the keypair's public key (base58)\n  - isMock flag is false\n- **Key Assertions:**\n  - `expect(result.current.connected).toBe(true)`\n  - `expect(result.current.publicKey?.toBase58()).toBe(keypair.publicKey.toBase58())`\n  - `expect(result.current.address).toBe(keypair.publicKey.toBase58())`\n  - `expect(result.current.isMock).toBe(false)`\n- **Imports:** Uses `useWallet` from wallet package, imports `TestWalletProvider`\n- **Mock Details:** Mocks `@solana/web3.js` Connection.getBalance to return 1 SOL without real RPC\n\n**Test Suite 2: MockWalletProvider (lines 53-68)**\n- **Test Name:** \"starts disconnected by default\"\n- **What It Verifies:**\n  - MockWalletProvider starts disconnected\n  - publicKey is null when disconnected\n  - address is null when disconnected\n  - isMock flag is true\n- **Key Assertions:**\n  - `expect(result.current.connected).toBe(false)`\n  - `expect(result.current.publicKey).toBeNull()`\n  - `expect(result.current.address).toBeNull()`\n  - `expect(result.current.isMock).toBe(true)`\n- **Imports:** Uses `useWallet` from wallet package, imports `MockWalletProvider`\n\n**Test Configuration:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/wallet/vitest.config.ts`\n- Environment: jsdom\n- Globals: enabled\n\n**Test Script:** `packages/wallet/package.json` line 23: `\"test\": \"vitest run\"`\n\n---\n\n### 2. Playwright E2E Tests (Platform App)\n\n#### 2.1 Visual Regression Tests\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/visual/states.spec.ts`\n\n**Test Suite: State variants (lines 3-132)**\n\n**Test 1: Home page - wallet disconnected (lines 5-12)**\n- **What It Verifies:** Home page renders correctly with disconnected wallet\n- **Key Actions:**\n  - Clears persisted wallet state from localStorage\n  - Takes screenshot of disconnected state\n- **Imports:** Uses fixtures from `../fixtures`\n\n**Test 2: Home page - wallet connected (lines 14-47)**\n- **What It Verifies:** Home page renders correctly after wallet connection\n- **Key Actions:**\n  - Clears localStorage\n  - Clicks wallet icon (`.rpg-wallet-icon`)\n  - Waits for connected state (`.rpg-wallet-icon--connected`)\n  - Re-freezes animations\n  - Takes screenshot\n- **Key Assertions:**\n  - Waits for `.rpg-wallet-icon--connected` selector (5s timeout)\n- **Imports:** Uses fixtures from `../fixtures`\n\n**Test 3: Profile page - wallet connected (lines 50-84)**\n- **What It Verifies:** Profile page renders correctly with connected wallet\n- **Key Actions:** Same as home connected test but on /profile route\n\n**Test 4: Coinflip page - wallet disconnected (lines 87-95)**\n- **What It Verifies:** Coinflip page renders correctly with disconnected wallet\n\n**Test 5: Coinflip page - wallet connected (lines 97-130)**\n- **What It Verifies:** Coinflip page renders correctly with connected wallet\n\n**Note:** All visual tests use the `stablePage` fixture which:\n- Seeds Math.random() and crypto.getRandomValues for determinism\n- Freezes Date.now()\n- Disables CSS/SVG animations\n- Waits for fonts and network idle\n- Collects console errors (fails test if any found)\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/visual/routes.spec.ts`\n\n**Test Suite: Route baselines (lines 3-63)**\n- Contains 11 route baseline tests (home, coinflip, lord-of-rngs, close-call, crash, game-of-trades, profile, quests, loot, fairness, leaderboard, 404)\n- Takes full-page screenshots of each route\n- Uses `stablePage` fixture for determinism\n- **Does not explicitly test wallet functionality but wallet icon is visible in all routes**\n\n#### 2.2 Real Mode Tests\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/real/startup.spec.ts`\n\n**Test Suite: Real mode startup (lines 27-72)**\n\n**Test 1: app loads without console errors and wallet icon renders disconnected (lines 28-44)**\n- **What It Verifies:**\n  - App loads without console errors\n  - Wallet icon is visible\n  - Wallet icon does NOT have connected class\n  - Balance displays \"—\" (em dash) for disconnected state\n- **Key Assertions:**\n  - `await expect(walletIcon).toBeVisible({ timeout: 10_000 })`\n  - `await expect(walletIcon).not.toHaveClass(/rpg-wallet-icon--connected/)`\n  - `await expect(amount).toHaveText(\"—\")`\n- **Selectors:**\n  - `.rpg-wallet-icon` (wallet icon)\n  - `.rpg-wallet-icon__amount` (balance display)\n\n**Test 2: clicking wallet icon calls connect without crashing (lines 46-71)**\n- **What It Verifies:**\n  - Clicking wallet icon triggers connect() without errors\n  - App remains functional after click\n  - Wallet icon and main app structure still visible\n- **Key Actions:**\n  - Clicks wallet icon\n  - Waits 1 second for processing\n  - Verifies wallet icon still visible\n  - Verifies main title still visible\n- **Key Assertions:**\n  - `await expect(walletIcon).toBeVisible()`\n  - `await expect(title).toBeVisible()`\n- **Selectors:**\n  - `.rpg-wallet-icon` (wallet icon)\n  - `.rpg-title` (main app title)\n\n**Test Fixture:** Uses custom `realPage` fixture (lines 8-25)\n- Collects console errors throughout test\n- Fails test if any console errors detected\n- Does NOT freeze randomness/time (real wallet needs real crypto)\n- Waits for network idle\n\n**Real Mode Config:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.real.config.ts`\n- Runs dev server on port 3001\n- Sets `VITE_MOCK_MODE=false`\n- Sets `VITE_RPC_URL=https://api.devnet.solana.com`\n- Test match pattern: `real/**/*.spec.ts`\n\n**Test Scripts:** `apps/platform/package.json`\n- Line 13: `\"test:visual\": \"playwright test\"`\n- Line 14: `\"test:visual:update\": \"playwright test --update-snapshots\"`\n- Line 15: `\"test:real\": \"playwright test --config playwright.real.config.ts\"`\n\n---\n\n### 3. Test Fixtures and Configuration\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/fixtures.ts`\n\n**Shared visual regression fixture: `stablePage` (lines 25-108)**\n- Extends base Playwright test\n- Seeds Math.random() with Mulberry32 PRNG (seed: 42)\n- Seeds crypto.getRandomValues for deterministic Keypair.generate()\n- Freezes Date.now() to fixed timestamp (2026-01-01T00:00:00Z)\n- Injects CSS to disable animations/transitions\n- Pauses SVG SMIL animations\n- Waits for fonts to load\n- Collects console errors and fails test if any found\n\n**File:** `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.config.ts`\n\n**Main Playwright config:**\n- Test directory: `./e2e`\n- Base URL: `http://localhost:3000`\n- Viewport: 1280x1080\n- Workers: 1 (serial execution)\n- Snapshot path template: `{testDir}/__snapshots__/{testFilePath}/{arg}{ext}`\n- Max diff pixel ratio: 0.015\n- Web server: `pnpm dev` on port 3000\n\n---\n\n### Summary of Test Coverage\n\n**Unit Tests (vitest):**\n- 2 test files found\n- 2 test suites\n- Tests cover TestWalletProvider auto-connect and MockWalletProvider disconnected state\n- Both test suites import from `@rng-utopia/wallet` package\n\n**E2E Tests (Playwright):**\n- 3 spec files found\n- 18 total test cases\n- Visual regression: 16 tests (11 route baselines + 5 state variants)\n- Real mode: 2 startup tests\n- All tests interact with wallet icon UI\n- Real mode