c, animations frozen)\n\n#### Visual State Tests (`e2e/visual/states.spec.ts`)\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/visual/states.spec.ts`\n\n- **Lines 1-132**: Full implementation\n- Tests wallet connected/disconnected states for:\n  - Home page (Lines 5-47)\n  - Profile page (Lines 50-85)\n  - Coinflip page (Lines 87-131)\n- **Mock wallet connect flow** (example Lines 14-46):\n  - Clears localStorage to ensure fresh state\n  - Clicks `.rpg-wallet-icon`\n  - Waits for `.rpg-wallet-icon--connected` selector\n  - Re-injects animation freeze CSS\n  - Takes screenshot\n\n#### Fixtures (`e2e/fixtures.ts`)\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/fixtures.ts`\n\n- **Lines 1-110**: Full implementation\n- **Lines 25-66**: `stablePage` fixture setup:\n  - Seeds Math.random with Mulberry32 (seed 42)\n  - Overrides crypto.getRandomValues for deterministic keypair generation\n  - Freezes Date.now to Jan 1, 2026\n- **Lines 68-97**: Overrides page.goto to:\n  - Wait for networkidle\n  - Inject animation-disabling CSS\n  - Pause SVG SMIL animations\n  - Wait for fonts.ready\n  - 300ms settle time\n- **Lines 100-106**: Console error collection and assertion\n\n---\n\n### 8. Package Scripts (`package.json`)\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/package.json`\n\n- **Line 13**: `\"test:visual\": \"playwright test\"`\n- **Line 14**: `\"test:visual:update\": \"playwright test --update-snapshots\"`\n- **Line 15**: `\"test:real\": \"playwright test --config playwright.real.config.ts\"`\n\n---\n\n### 9. Wallet Package Architecture\n\n#### WalletProvider (`packages/wallet/src/WalletProvider.tsx`)\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/wallet/src/WalletProvider.tsx`\n\n- **Lines 29-36**: `isMockMode()` checks `VITE_MOCK_MODE` env var\n  - Returns `true` if undefined, empty, or \"true\"\n  - Returns `false` only if explicitly \"false\"\n- **Lines 42-54**: Unified pr