a)\n\n### Test Infrastructure\n✅ **Visual tests** (`playwright.config.ts`):\n- Mock mode (default)\n- Deterministic fixtures (seeded PRNG, frozen time, no animations)\n- 11 route baselines + 3 state variants\n\n✅ **Real wallet tests** (`playwright.real.config.ts`):\n- Separate port (3001)\n- Forces `VITE_MOCK_MODE=false` via env override\n- 2 startup tests (app loads disconnected, connect doesn't crash)\n\n### Test Scripts\n✅ **package.json** provides:\n- `test:visual` → visual regression tests (mock mode)\n- `test:visual:update` → update snapshots\n- `test:real` → real wallet mode startup tests"}],"totalDurationMs":129447,"totalTokens":76061,"totalToolUseCount":27,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":322,"cache_read_input_tokens":71056,"output_tokens":4678,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":322,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
