{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_014WYEXy8UZHcTHr1TKBXsc3","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Gap Analysis Complete: 205-real-wallet\n\n- **Satisfied**: 20 / 22\n- **Deferred**: 0\n- **Gaps**: 2 (critical: 0, moderate: 1, low: 1)\n\n### Gaps Found\n\n1. **FR-2.2 — Balance updates after transactions** (low): No explicit `refresh()` call after `sendTransaction` in CoinflipContext. Balance relies on 10-second polling, so post-transaction balance updates are delayed. Fix: call `useBalance().refresh()` after each transaction.\n\n2. **FR-3.3 — Transaction confirmation awaited before UI update** (moderate): `sendTransaction` returns after sending the transaction to the network, but no `confirmTransaction` call follows. UI state (match fetching, active match setting) updates immediately, before on-chain confirmation. Fix: add `await connection.confirmTransaction(signature, 'confirmed')` before fetching match state.\n\n### Files Written\n\n- **Report**: `docs/specs/205-real-wallet/gap-analysis.md`\n- **Spec annotations**: `docs/specs/205-real-wallet/spec.md` — FR checkboxes updated with HTML comment evidence\n\nSpec FR checkboxes updated with evidence annotations."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":323,"cache_read_input_tokens":86091,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":323},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0f6af63c-d689-426d-9dd8-218925b8488a","uuid":"53d10fd3-0620-4dac-b243-80759a0f1247"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":344513,"duration_api_ms":586146,"num_turns":29,"result":"## Gap Analysis Complete: 205-real-wallet\n\n- **Satisfied**: 20 / 22\n- **Deferred**: 0\n- **Gaps**: 2 (critical: 0, moderate: 1, low: 1)\n\n### Gaps Found\n\n1. **FR-2.2 — Balance updates after transactions** (low): No explicit `refresh()` call after `sendTransaction` in CoinflipContext. Balance relies on 10-second polling, so post-transaction balance updates are delayed. Fix: call `useBalance().refresh()` after each transaction.\n\n2. **FR-3.3 — Transaction confirmation awaited before UI update** (moderate): `sendTransaction` returns after sending the transaction to the network, but no `confirmTransaction` call follows. UI state (match fetching, active match setting) updates immediately, before on-chain confirmation. Fix: add `await connection.confirmTransaction(signature, 'confirmed')` before fetching match state.\n\n### Files Written\n\n- **Report**: `docs/specs/205-real-wallet/gap-analysis.md`\n- **Spec annotations**: `docs/specs/205-real-wallet/spec.md` — FR checkboxes updated with HTML comment evidence\n\nSpec FR checkboxes updated with evidence annotations.","stop_reason":null,"session_id":"0f6af63c-d689-426d-9dd8-218925b8488a","total_cost_usd":2.9835074999999995,"usage":{"input_tokens":19,"cache_creation_input_tokens":72727,"cache_read_input_tokens":988906,"output_tokens":11347,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":72727,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":10966,"outputTokens":673,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.014331,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000},"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":19,"outputTokens":11347,"cacheReadInputTokens":988906,"cacheCreationInputToke